comments.content: This canvas tests the layout of decorators. They show the four possible decorator positions.
This node does not have any decorators.
These two nodes have decorators that are hot spots. Clicking them should output a decorationHandler() message to the test harness console.
These two nodes have view only decorators
This node shows a decorator with a zoom-in image and a yellow background rectangle.
This node has a decorator at a custom position of x = -10 y = -10
This node has two label decorators
This node should show 9 rectangle decorators each positioned at 0,0 offset from the 9 'anchor' points around the node.
